The question is asking for the league that the New York men's soccer team has played in, excluding the National Premier Soccer League (NPSL). To answer this, I need to query the "Soccer Team Performance Table" and filter out any rows where the "League" is "NPSL." Then, I will extract the unique league names from the remaining rows.

I will now execute the SQL query to find the leagues that the New York men's soccer team has played in, excluding NPSL.
